If a spell or ability an opponent controls causes you to discard Sigarda, Dawn of Mercy, put it onto the battlefield instead of putting it into your graveyard.

When Pulse Seeker enters, create a 1/1 black and red Vampire creature token with menace.
Equipped creature gets +1/+0.
Equip {1}

Exsanguinator enters with X pain counters on it.
Whenever equipped creature attacks, each opponent loses X life and you gain X life, where X is the number of pain counters on Exsanguinator.
